main event: Several sightings of unidentified flying objects were reported in Middletown, New York in April 1965 and April 1966.
interesting points: The object on 22 April 1965 was observed for 3-5 minutes with an irregular course,The second sighting on 25 April 1966 involved three witnesses, whose reliability was considered very good,The object observed on 25 April 1966 was described as large, greenish, with lights around its perimeter and moved in a jerky manner,The reports concluded there was insufficient data for evaluation of the incidents, No photographs or physical evidence were recorded in either case.
